text: Tomás Couve Correa (born 30 June 1972) is a Chilean equestrian. He competed in two events at the 2012 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1972 births Category:Living people Category:Chilean male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Chile Category:Equestrians at the 2012 Summer Olympics Category:Equestrians at the 2011 Pan American Games Category:Sportspeople from Santiago
